Business Fundamentals Workshop — Successfully Concluded!
Our exclusive session on Career Opportunities in Grameenphone, Requirements & Business Modality wrapped up successfully, offering participants a deep dive into the corporate landscape.
A heartfelt thanks to our Resource Person, Nadim Shariar,
Regional Head, Grameenphone – Rajshahi,
for sharing practical insights, career guidance, and a clear understanding of Grameenphone’s business model and professional opportunities.
Participants gained firsthand knowledge and valuable direction to shape their future careers in one of the country’s leading telecom companies.
Thank you to everyone who joined and contributed to the success of this session!  